{"tid":1707180,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"成班人係度做乜？","createTime":"2019-11-11T09:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T09:07:15.000Z","uid":331975,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"0e833115b92d357fdd944d2af3bb99682474cd16","tid":1707180,"uid":331975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:03:49.000Z","msg":"p牌第一次開post  <br />\n對於今日行動有建議<br />\n今朝一直都做得好，係事實<br />\n可能因為搞突破，對方係冇部署<br />\n但係到咗而家，港島聚緊人成班手足企係馬路<br />\n我想問，企係度做乜，記唔記得屠龍小隊有講過要主動出擊先得。<br />\n每次我地就係企係度等人多，好啦夠人多，就冇下一步，永遠我地做等對方set好部署，不斷係唔同方向包炒，到最後又係傷既多，實際做到既事唔多。無論小區戰定港島又好，我地應該要夠人就主動出擊，令到對方冇時間部署。<br />\n成五個月我地都係等啲狗嚟清場先行動，我地要主動打亂對方陣腳。<br />\n每次企係度同對方對峙，對方一推進，我地就跑散囇，人地已經熟咗尼套玩法。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"},{"pid":"726401a4d58a9bdacd6c05e91cee764a0a947ca9","tid":1707180,"uid":331975,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:06:39.000Z","msg":"p牌啊 <br />\n推唔郁<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79e1223b50542ff2aa3d46eb5bd4b9e97cc285d9","tid":1707180,"uid":210205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T09:07:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src